library(dplyr)
##

gapminder %>%
  filter(lifeExp >=70 )%>% 
  group_by(continent) %>% 
  summarise( n= n() ) %>%                         #   
  ggplot(aes(x=continent,y=n,fill=continent)) +            #geom_point(aes(color=Month)) +   #   244  
  labs(title=" 70   ()", x="",y="")+
  #geom_bar(stat="identity)                                                       
  geom_col()

  filter(lifeExp >=70 )%>%                           
  group_by(continent) %>% 
  summarise( n= n_distinct(country) ) %>%    # ' '.                         ####
  ggplot(aes(x=continent,y=n,fill=continent)) +    
  labs(title=" 70    ", x="continent" ,y="")+
  #geom_bar(stat="identity)
